ActCustoms Tariff
SubjectOrder Amending the Schedule to the Customs Tariff (Harmonized System, 2017)
PrecisOrder Amending the SCHEDULE TO THE CUSTOMS TARIFF (HARMONIZED SYSTEM, 2017) in order to make the necessary changes to the Customs Tariff to fulfill Canada’s international obligations as a signatory to the Convention. All signatories, including Canada’s major trading partners such as the United States and the European Union, are also updating their tariff schedules to reflect the updated Harmonized System effective January 1, 2017.
